Texts.Eng:
Bread. Pickles. Onion. Lettuce. Nondescript meat analogue. Ketchup. Bread. It's a staple classic of humanity's unhealthiness. There are other burgers out there. But this one is special. Maybe.

面包。泡菜。洋葱。生菜。非描述性肉类类似物。番茄酱。面包。这是人类不健康的典型代表。外面还有其他汉堡。但这个很特别。也许 吧。
